<h3><span class="mw-headline" id="PDA">PDA</span><span class="mw-editsection"><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">[</span><a href="/w/index.php?title=Amstrad&amp;action=edit&amp;section=14" title="Edit section: PDA">edit</a><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">]</span></span></h3>
<ul>
<li><b><a href="/wiki/PenPad" title="PenPad">PDA 600 Pen Pad</a></b> (1993, Z8S180 CPU)</li>
</ul>
<h3><span class="mw-headline" id="Set-top_box">Set-top box</span><span class="mw-editsection"><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">[</span><a href="/w/index.php?title=Amstrad&amp;action=edit&amp;section=15" title="Edit section: Set-top box">edit</a><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">]</span></span></h3>
<ul>
<li><b>Amstrad Sky box</b> <b>DRX100</b> (2001), <b>DRX200</b> (2001), <b>DRX300</b> (2003), <b>DRX400</b> (2004), <b>DRX500</b> (2004), <b>DRX550</b>, (2006)</li>
<li><b>Amstrad Sky+ box</b> <b>DRX280</b> (2003)</li>
<li><b>Amstrad Sky+HD box</b> <b>DRX780</b> (2007), <b>DRX895</b> (2009)</li>
<li><b>Amstrad Sky HD Multiroom Receiver</b> <b>DRX595</b> (2011)</li>
</ul>
